# SRT Prompt Generator — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

Dashboard-style Python application converting SRT subtitle files into AI-generated image/video prompts with batch processing.

## Project Structure

```
1.Prompt_Image/
├── main.py                      # Entry point
├── config.json                  # App settings
├── api_keys.json                # API keys (separate)
├── requirements.txt             # Dependencies
├── styles/
│   ├── Cinematic.txt            # Film-style preset
│   └── Documentary.txt          # Documentary preset
├── core/
│   ├── srt_parser.py            # Parse SRT + group by interval
│   ├── api_client.py            # Multi-endpoint API + fallback
│   ├── prompt_generator.py      # Generate prompts via API
│   └── process_controller.py    # Batch queue + Start/Pause/Stop
└── ui/
    ├── main_window.py           # Main dashboard layout
    ├── settings_dialog.py       # API Settings popup
    ├── config_section.py        # Style, Output, Tier, Threads
    ├── projects_section.py      # Batch projects table
    ├── srt_preview.py           # SRT file preview
    ├── actions_section.py       # Process / Stop / Retry buttons
    └── log_section.py           # Processing log + status bar
```

## Verification Results

| Test | Status | Details |
|------|--------|---------|
| SRT Parser | ✅ Pass | Parsed 3 segments, grouped into 2 groups (5s interval) |
| API Client Config | ✅ Pass | Loads primary + 1 fallback endpoint from [api_keys.json](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/api_keys.json) |
| Style Scanner | ✅ Pass | Detects `['Cinematic', 'Documentary']` from `/styles` folder |
| App Launch | ✅ Pass | GUI runs without errors (dark mode, all sections visible) |

## How to Run

```bash
cd "F:\1. Edit Videos\8.AntiCode\1.Prompt_Image\1.Prompt_Image"
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py
```

## Key Features

- **Batch processing** — Scan Folder to import all `.srt` files at once, Process ALL
- **Multi-endpoint API** — Auto-fallback when rate limited (429)
- **Style presets** — Drop [.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/requirements.txt) files in `/styles`, auto-detected in dropdown
- **Process control** — Start / Pause / Stop / Retry Failed
- **Output** — Auto-saves [.txt](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/requirements.txt) + `.csv` per project to output folder
- **Restart Tool** — One-click app restart for code updates
- **Settings popup** — API config, theme, dependencies (separate from main UI)
